      "body": "> > Hi folks, this should be fixed in Abctl `v0.29.0`. Please give it a try.\n> \n> this version fixed it for us - but I havent tried newer builds\n\nI was installing on 0.30.0 with no success, i had to use values.yaml \n\n```\n\nglobal:\n  auth:\n    cookieSecureSetting: \"false\"\n    security:\n      cookieSecureSetting: \"false\"\n\nserver:\n  extraEnv:\n    - name: AB_COOKIE_SECURE\n      value: \"false\"\n    - name: AB_COOKIE_SAME_SITE\n      value: \"Lax\"\n```",
